trans-unit.source: Provides data for the <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartAdded" />, <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartDeleted" />, <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartClosed" />, <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartMoved" />, and <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.SelectedWebPartChanged" /> events.
trans-unit.target: 提供 <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartAdded" />、<see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartDeleted" />、<see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartClosed" />、<see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartMoved" /> 以及 <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.SelectedWebPartChanged" /> 事件的資料。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartEventArgs> class contains information for several different Web Parts events.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartEventArgs>類別包含數個不同的 Web 組件事件的資訊。

trans-unit.source: These events include the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartAdded>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartDeleted>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartClosed>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartMoved>, and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.SelectedWebPartChanged> events.
The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartEventArgs> class provides access to the Web Parts control involved in the event.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartEventArgs>類別提供參與事件之 Web 組件控制項的存取。

trans-unit.source: The Web Parts control is accessed through the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartEventArgs.WebPart%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Web 組件控制項透過存取<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartEventArgs.WebPart%2A>屬性。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart" /> (or server or user control) involved in the event.
trans-unit.target: 事件中所包含的 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart" /> (或伺服器或使用者控制項)。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartEventArgs" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartEventArgs" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: Gets the Web Parts control involved in the event.
trans-unit.target: 取得事件中所包含的 Web 組件控制項。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart" /> involved in a <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartAdded" />, <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartDeleted" />, <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartClosed" />, <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartMoved" />, or <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.SelectedWebPartChanged" /> event.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart" />、<see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartAdded" />、<see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartDeleted" />、<see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartClosed" /> 或 <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartMoved" /> 事件中所包含的 <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.SelectedWebPartChanged" />。
